{"tid":404400,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"夏世三真係好癲","createTime":"2017-09-18T05:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T06:20:57.000Z","uid":23305,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e953ba5afc4c50bb3ecaa04b7af1f4bb45353cd8","tid":404400,"uid":23305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:46:08.000Z","msg":"睇完琴晚夏神短短出黎廿分鐘 真係好屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb8b25ab7952dba761dd11c10958fbad802d9ef","tid":404400,"uid":125665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完琴晚夏神短短出黎廿分鐘 真係好屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢個下推到禁區頂射門仲以為會入 明明係食糊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21c14a2f15ff1d1f8890f28791375f794a924ee","tid":404400,"uid":23305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇完琴晚夏神短短出黎廿分鐘 真係好屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢個下推到禁區頂射門仲以為會入 明明係食糊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都以為係 但每次見佢攞波做都有種與別不同嘅感覺"},{"pid":"e7529bd7954811bcc20cd0f3819345f6ea1d2721","tid":404400,"uid":15140,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇完琴晚夏神短短出黎廿分鐘 真係好屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢個下推到禁區頂射門仲以為會入 明明係食糊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n世三臨射之時 望一望施治<br />\n睇施眼有淚光 世三唔忍心射入<br />\n將皮球輕輕射高 讓施治輕鬆接實<br />\n之後雙方互望一眼 手拖手走進更衣場了"},{"pid":"cf31fa0affd252b4b2141aa3fdd7873eaaa10640","tid":404400,"uid":72946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇完琴晚夏神短短出黎廿分鐘 真係好屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢個下推到禁區頂射門仲以為會入 明明係食糊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n世三臨射之時 望一望施治<br />\n睇施眼有淚光 世三唔忍心射入<br />\n將皮球輕輕射高 讓施治輕鬆接實<br />\n之後雙方互望一眼 手拖手走進更衣場殘廁了</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6b0023d35b37506b9f03edf312f19c37880f35f2","tid":404400,"uid":23305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:20:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇完琴晚夏神短短出黎廿分鐘 真係好屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢個下推到禁區頂射門仲以為會入 明明係食糊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n世三臨射之時 望一望施治<br />\n睇施眼有淚光 世三唔忍心射入<br />\n將皮球輕輕射高 讓施治輕鬆接實<br />\n之後雙方互望一眼 手拖手走進更衣場了</blockquote><br />\n但果下雖然冇角度 但係球速都唔慢 施治咁都接得實"}]}